      </div>
      <div class="border-t border-forest-700 pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-3 text-xs text-forest-400">
        <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} 413Septic.com — Western Massachusetts Septic Guide</p>
        <p>Built by <a href="https://banaswebdesign.com" class="text-forest-300 hover:text-white">Banas Web Design</a></p>
